%N A397662 Decimal expansion of Sum_{k>=1} (zeta(4) - H(k,4)) * H(k)/k, where H(k) = A001008(k)/A002805(k) is the k-th harmonic number, and H(k,4) = A007410(k)/A007480(k) is the k-th generalized harmonic number of order 4.
